What is CloudFront?
CloudFront is AWS Content Delivery Network (CDN).
It delivers content from the nearest Edge Location.

Why CloudFront?

Without CDN:

India User
     ↓
US Server

High latency.

With CDN:

India User
     ↓
Nearest Edge Location

Fast delivery.

Components:
Origin

Source of content.

Examples:

S3 Bucket
EC2
Load Balancer
Edge Location

Caches content closer to users.

Real-Time Scenario:

Netflix-like Application

Users
   ↓
CloudFront
   ↓
S3

Video loads faster globally.

Benefits
Faster Website
Reduced Server Load
DDoS Protection
SSL Support
